documentation.text:
The consumer reports when they returned the vehicle but requires the rental company to provide
 a validation timestamp to the consumer inorder for the return to be accepted. This prevents
 a consumer from reporting a vehicle is returned witout a company verifying the vehicle has been returned.

returnRental(uint256,uint256,uint256).notice: The consumer reports when they returned the vehicle but requires the rental company to provide a validation timestamp to the consumer inorder for the return to be accepted. This prevents a consumer from reporting a vehicle is returned witout a company verifying the vehicle has been returned.
